AS A RESULT OF SYSTEM ENHANCEMENTS, 30 DAYS PAST DUE AS A % OF TOTAL, NET WRITE-OFF RATE (PRINCIPAL ONLY) AND NET WRITE-OFF RATE (PRINCIPAL AND FEES) HAVE BEEN PRESENTED.

(F)

