BECAUSE WE CONSIDER UNCOLLECTIBLE INTEREST AND/OR FEES IN OUR RESERVES FOR CREDIT LOSSES, A NET WRITE-OFF RATE INCLUDING PRINCIPAL, INTEREST AND/OR FEES IS ALSO PRESENTED. THE TWELVE MONTHS ENDED DECEMBER 31, 2015 REFLECT THE IMPACT OF A CHANGE

IN THE TIMING OF CHARGE-OFFS FOR CARD MEMBER RECEIVABLES AND LOANS IN CERTAIN MODIFICATION PROGRAMS FROM 180 DAYS PAST DUE TO 120 DAYS PAST DUE.

