EXPENSES

MARKETING, PROMOTION, REWARDS, CARD MEMBER SERVICES AND OTHER EXPENSES DECREASED $217 MILLION OR 10 PERCENT IN 2015 COMPARED TO 2014, BUT INCREASED 3 PERCENT ON AN FX-ADJUSTED BASIS, REFLECTING

