AS OF SEPTEMBER 30, 2015, AND PROSPECTIVELY, CERTAIN INTERCOMPANY BALANCES HAVE BEEN RECLASSIFIED BETWEEN OPERATING SEGMENTS, AS A RESULT OF SYSTEMS

