PRIMARILY DUE TO THE IMPACT OF THE BUSINESS TRAVEL JOINT VENTURE TRANSACTION (RESULTING IN A LACK OF COMPARABILITY BETWEEN PERIODS), PARTIALLY OFFSET BY ELEVATED LEVEL OF SPENDING ON GROWTH INITIATIVES IN 2015.

