JOINT VENTURE TRANSACTION (RESULTING IN A LACK OF COMPARABILITY BETWEEN PERIODS), INCLUDING THE GAIN ASSOCIATED WITH THE TRANSACTION IN THE SECOND QUARTER OF 2014, PARTIALLY OFFSET BY TRANSACTION-RELATED COSTS AND RESTRUCTURING CHARGES.

