AND 2013, RESPECTIVELY) BY (II) ONE-YEAR AVERAGE SEGMENT CAPITAL ($2.3 BILLION, $2.0 BILLION AND $2.1 BILLION FOR 2015, 2014 AND 2013, RESPECTIVELY). RETURN ON AVERAGE TANGIBLE SEGMENT CAPITAL, A NON-GAAP MEASURE, IS COMPUTED IN THE SAME MANNER

