THE FULLY PHASED-IN BASEL III COMMON EQUITY TIER 1 AND TIER 1 RISK-BASED CAPITAL RATIOS, NON-GAAP MEASURES, ARE CALCULATED AS COMMON EQUITY TIER 1 OR TIER 1

CAPITAL UNDER FULLY PHASED-IN BASEL III RULES, AS APPLICABLE, DIVIDED BY RISK-WEIGHTED ASSETS UNDER FULLY PHASED-IN BASEL III RULES. REFER TO TABLE 20 FOR A RECONCILIATION OF COMMON EQUITY TIER 1 AND TIER 1 CAPITAL UNDER FULLY PHASED-IN BASEL III

