NOTES ARE ADJUSTED TO REFLECT THE IMPACT OF CHANGES IN FAIR VALUE DUE TO CHANGES IN INTEREST RATES. REFER TO NOTE 14 FOR MORE DETAILS ON THE COMPANYS TREATMENT OF FAIR VALUE HEDGES.

