SEPTEMBER 1, 2066, EXCEPT IN THE CASE OF EITHER (I) A PRIOR REDEMPTION OR (II) A DEFAULT. AT THE COMPANYS OPTION, THE SUBORDINATED DEBENTURES ARE REDEEMABLE FOR CASH ON OR AFTER SEPTEMBER 1, 2016, AT 100 PERCENT OF THE

PRINCIPAL AMOUNTS PLUS ANY ACCRUED BUT UNPAID INTEREST.

