STOCK OPTIONS

EACH STOCK OPTION HAS AN EXERCISE PRICE EQUAL TO THE MARKET PRICE OF THE COMPANYS COMMON STOCK ON THE DATE OF

GRANT AND A CONTRACTUAL TERM OF 10 YEARS FROM THE DATE OF GRANT. STOCK OPTIONS GENERALLY VEST 100 PERCENT ON THE THIRD ANNIVERSARY OF THE GRANT DATE.

