2014, AND REQUIRE MANAGEMENT JUDGMENT. THESE FIGURES MAY NOT BE INDICATIVE OF FUTURE FAIR VALUES, NOR CAN THE FAIR VALUE OF THE COMPANY BE ESTIMATED BY AGGREGATING THE AMOUNTS PRESENTED.

