(A)

THE COMPANYS UNVESTED RESTRICTED STOCK AWARDS, WHICH INCLUDE THE RIGHT TO RECEIVE NON-FORFEITABLE DIVIDENDS OR DIVIDEND EQUIVALENTS, ARE CONSIDERED

PARTICIPATING SECURITIES. CALCULATIONS OF EPS UNDER THE TWO-CLASS METHOD EXCLUDE FROM THE NUMERATOR ANY DIVIDENDS PAID OR OWED ON PARTICIPATING SECURITIES AND ANY UNDISTRIBUTED EARNINGS CONSIDERED TO BE ATTRIBUTABLE TO PARTICIPATING SECURITIES. THE

RELATED PARTICIPATING SECURITIES ARE SIMILARLY EXCLUDED FROM THE DENOMINATOR.

