2015, REFLECTS THE IMPACT OF A CHANGE IN THE TIMING OF CHARGE-OFFS FOR CARD MEMBER LOANS IN CERTAIN MODIFICATION PROGRAMS FROM 180 DAYS PAST DUE TO 120 DAYS PAST DUE, WHICH WAS FULLY RECOGNIZED DURING THE THREE MONTHS ENDED MARCH 31, 2015.

